data.name: label2.Text
data.value: You can manage here all your planet palettes for Space Engine 0.971 here. Add, remove, change weight for each individual palette, and have them changed in Space Engine! You can also export your modifications, add a picture and a color and there you go, you can send the file! With this tool, a backup is made everytime a change is made, so you can mess around without being too much worried.
